                            <p class="rating-count">342 verified reviews</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="price-large">
                        <p class="price-label">From</p>
                        <p class="price-amount-large">€145 <span>/ night</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <button class="book-direct-btn-large" onclick="window.open('https://hotelandeaterywest.com/book', '_blank')">
                        Book Direct
                    </button>
                    <p class="direct-note">You'll book directly on the hotel's website</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- =============================================
                 VERIFIED INFO — THE HONEST TRUTH
                 ============================================= -->
            <div class="content-card full-width verified-section">
                <h3 class="card-title verified">✓ Verified Information — The Honest Truth</h3>
                <div class="verified-grid">
                    <div class="verified-item">
                        <div class="verified-icon">🚗</div>
                        <div class="verified-content">
                            <h4>Parking</h4>
                            <p><span class="highlight">Street parking only</span> — €4.00/hour. Nearest spot typically 50m walk. No private garage. Consider P+R if driving.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="verified-item">
                        <div class="verified-icon">🥐</div>
                        <div class="verified-content">
                            <h4>Breakfast</h4>
                            <p><span class="highlight">Available but not included</span> — €18/person. Full breakfast served in ground-floor restaurant, 7:30-10:30am.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="verified-item">
                        <div class="verified-icon">📶</div>
                        <div class="verified-content">
                            <h4>WiFi</h4>
                            <p><span class="highlight">Fast & free</span> — 100+ Mbps throughout hotel. Suitable for video calls and remote work.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="verified-item">
                        <div class="verified-icon">🚊</div>
                        <div class="verified-content">
                            <h4>Transport</h4>
                            <p><span class="highlight">Tram 7 & 13</span> — Stop "Baarsjesweg" is 2 min walk. Direct connection to Central Station (12 min).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CONTENT GRID -->
            <div class="content-grid">

                <!-- DESCRIPTION -->
                <div class="content-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">✦ About This Hotel</h3>
                    <div class="description-text">
                        <p>Hotel & Eatery West combines industrial-chic design with warm hospitality. The ground-floor restaurant serves locally-sourced meals, while upstairs rooms feature curated art and dedicated workspaces.</p>
                        <p>Located steps from the trendy Baarsjes neighborhood, you're surrounded by independent coffee shops, vintage stores, and authentic local life.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- BEST FOR -->
                <div class="content-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">✦ Best For</h3>
                    <div class="best-for-list">
                        <span class="best-for-item">Digital nomads</span>
                        <span class="best-for-item">Couples</span>
                        <span class="best-for-item">Design enthusiasts</span>
                        <span class="best-for-item">Remote workers</span>
                        <span class="best-for-item">Foodies</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- AMENITIES -->
                <div class="content-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">✦ Amenities</h3>
                    <div class="amenities-grid">
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">📶</span>
                            <span>Fast WiFi</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">💻</span>
                            <span>In-room workspace</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">🍽️</span>
                            <span>Restaurant</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">☕</span>
                            <span>Coffee maker</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">❄️</span>
                            <span>Air conditioning</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">🔒</span>
                            <span>Safe</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">👔</span>
                            <span>Ironing</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">🧴</span>
                            <span>Luxury toiletries</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="amenity-item">
                            <span class="amenity-icon">📺</span>
                            <span>Smart TV</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- NEIGHBORHOOD -->
                <div class="content-card">
                    <h3 class="card-title">✦ The Neighborhood</h3>
                    <p class="neighborhood-text">
                        Amsterdam West is where locals actually live. Skip the tourist traps and discover the city's creative heart — full of independent cafes, galleries, and some of the best food in the city.
                    </p>
                    <div class="nearby-list">
                        <div class="nearby-item">
                            <span>☕ Lot Sixty One Coffee</span>
                            <span class="distance">3 min</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="nearby-item">
                            <span>🍜 Fou Fow Ramen</span>
                            <span class="distance">5 min</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="nearby-item">
                            <span>🌳 Westerpark</span>
