            </div>

            <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
            <div class="bottom-cta">
                <h3>Ready to book <em>directly?</em></h3>
                <p>Skip the middleman. 100% of your payment goes to the hotel.</p>
                <button class="book-direct-btn-large" onclick="window.open('https://hotelandeaterywest.com/book', '_blank')">
                    Book Direct — Best Price Guaranteed
